## üé® Design Token System

### Color Philosophy
```css
/* Semantic Color Tokens - Automatically adapt to light/dark mode */
:root {
  --bg: 248 248 250;          /* Background canvas */
  --surface: 255 255 255;     /* Cards, panels, elevated surfaces */
  --label: 17 17 17;          /* Primary text */
  --label-sec: 90 90 92;      /* Secondary text */
  --separator: 0 0 0 / 0.08;  /* Borders, dividers */
  --fill: 118 118 128 / 0.12; /* Input backgrounds, subtle fills */
  --accent: 0 122 255;        /* CTA buttons, links, highlights */
}

@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --bg: 20 20 22;           /* Deep dark background */
    --surface: 28 28 30;      /* Elevated dark surfaces */
    --label: 242 242 247;     /* High contrast text */
    --label-sec: 198 198 200; /* Muted text */
    --separator: 255 255 255 / 0.12; /* Subtle borders */
    --fill: 235 235 245 / 0.16;      /* Dark fills */
    --accent: 10 132 255;     /* Brighter accent for dark mode */
  }
}
```

### Typography System
```css
/* Apple-inspired Font Stack */
--font-sans: ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 
             "Segoe UI", Roboto, Inter, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
--font-mono: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, 
             "Cascadia Mono", "Segoe UI Mono", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", monospace;
```

**Typography Hierarchy:**
- **Title**: 18px, semibold - Major headings (emptyTitle)
- **Headline**: 16px, medium - Section headers, button labels
- **Body**: 14px, regular - Main content, chat bubbles
- **Caption**: 12px, regular - Metadata, timestamps (smallLabel, metaRow)

### Spacing & Layout System
```css
/* 8px Grid System */
--radius: 12px;    /* Standard border radius */
--blur: 20px;      /* Backdrop blur intensity */
--duration: 180ms; /* Animation duration */
--easing: cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1); /* Natural easing curve */

/* Touch Targets: Minimum 44x44px for accessibility */
.button { min-height: 44px; }
.input { min-height: 44px; }
```

### Elevation & Shadows
```css
/* Light Mode Shadow */
--shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);

/* Dark Mode Shadow - More prominent for depth */
--shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.45), 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
```

