**Animation Design:**
```css
@keyframes blink {
  0%, 80%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; }  /* Subtle, non-distracting */
  40% { opacity: 0.8; }
}
.dot { 
  animation: blink 1s infinite;     /* Natural timing */
  animation-delay: 0.2s increments; /* Staggered effect */
}
```

**Apple Principles Applied:**
- **Subtle Motion**: Animation is purposeful, not decorative
- **Reduced Motion Support**: Respects system accessibility preferences
- **Visual Hierarchy**: Indicator is clearly secondary to content

