## üåà Theme Implementation

### Automatic Theme Switching
The design system automatically adapts to user's system preference:
```css
:root { /* Light mode defaults */ }
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root { /* Dark mode overrides */ }
}
```

### Color Contrast Compliance
- **Light Mode**: Meets WCAG AA standards (4.5:1 contrast ratio)
- **Dark Mode**: Enhanced contrast for better readability
- **Accent Colors**: Adjusted brightness for each theme

